Package: CNVExpression
Type: Package
Title: Integration of Copy Number Variations with Gene Expression Analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bruno Rodrigo", "Assuncao",
           email = "bruno.assuncao@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")))
Description: CNVExpression provides a comprehensive workflow for integrating
    Copy Number Variation (CNV) data with gene expression data. The package
    enables identification of genes whose expression levels are significantly
    affected by copy number alterations. It leverages the CNVRanger package
    for population-level CNV analysis and provides functions for data
    preprocessing, CNV-expression correlation analysis, result filtering,
    and gene annotation. Designed for cancer genomics studies, particularly
    useful for TCGA data analysis.
